Song 22
   \tHave faith in God - 2
   \tHave faith in God for the answer
   \tHave faith in God.

1. Faith in God can move a mighty mountain;
   Faith in God can calm the troubled sea;
   Faith can make the desert like a fountain;
   Faith in God brings victory. - Have

2. Faith in God will take us over Jordan;
   Without death we live eternally;
   Christ Jesus for us has paid the ransom;
   Faith in God brings victory. - Have

3. God has come to live and dwell among us;
   He is hid in all simplicity;
   He will lead us ever like a shepherd;
   Faith in God brings victory. - Have
